    "created_at": "2016-06-06T02:13:55Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-06-06T02:13:55Z",
    "body": "We don't add built-in APIs for `toggleXXX`, since it can be simply achieved with existing APIs. For frameworks it is usually bad to have many ways to do the same thing.\n\nFor `toggleDevTools`, it exists only because we implemented it before `isDevToolsOpened` and `openDevTools`, it is was a design mistake a few years ago when we started Electron project.\n"
